cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.GT. 

The paper proposes a scalable algorithm for multiclass node classification in weighted graphs. This problem is related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data structures (cs.DS). The algorithm is based on a game-theoretic formulation of the problem (cs.GT) and is evaluated on real-world data (cs.SI).
